I can't really help with dinos specifically, but I can offer some good lizzer stories:

>A spare in the trunk
Homeless kobold taken home, and helps a semi depressed man get his shit together. Shenanigans ensue. Upbeat slice of life vibe.

>Forgotten places
Alien lizard woman and a walking Irish stereotype man get blackmailed into exploring the backrooms together. Action heavy hurt/comfort vibe.

>Broken sanctuary
A stone age tribal raptor from a matriarchal society saves a marooned scientist from a crash, and they survive together in the jungles of 'nam. Gritty woodland vibes.

>Unlikely bride
Conan the barbarian has an arranged marriage with an ESL kobold and they go on a journey for political reasons. 80s movie sword and sorcery vibes.

That's it for the thread stories that I can think of. Snekguys valbaran stories are also decent, as well as his one shots like conjunction and heart of the mountain.
